net.objectzoo.ebc.util

Class Pair<T1,T2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.objectzoo.ebc.util.Pair<T1,T2>
  • Type Parameters:
    T1 - the type of the pairs first item
    T2 - the type of the pairs second item

    public class Pair<T1,T2>
extends java.lang.Object
    A Pair is a container combining two other objects of known types. The Pair can be used as output of an EBC if more than a single object has to be the result.
    Author:
    tilmann
